text: Does anyone know if HUB db looking to be an add-on or included? Basic, standard etc. TY
Hi <@U26CZR9MW>. HubDB is included for customers who have/purchase the Website Add-on.

The one that comes with 3000 visitors?
We’re having some conversations internally whether it will be included in both versions, so this may change, but as of right now yes it will be included in Website Starter and Website.
Okay thank you, so we we are going to be ‘quoting' you (haha) on a project we are starting today. It is critical to this client at the starter level :slightly_smiling_face: Thank you in advance.
